diff --git a/analytics_docs.md b/analytics_docs.md
index 24edf16..1b2c474 100644
--- a/analytics_docs.md
+++ b/analytics_docs.md
@@ -19,3 +19,14 @@ Since each analytics platform has different setup instructions, we've created a
 Follow the [Google Analytics Guide](https://support.google.com/analytics/answer/9304153?hl=en) to add Google Analytics to your project.
 
 The ideal place to add Google Analytics is in `src/routes/+layout.svelte`.
+
+### Zenovay
+
+Set `PUBLIC_ZENOVAY_TRACKING_CODE` to the `ZV_...` code from your Zenovay
+website settings. The root layout initializes cookieless tracking and records
+SvelteKit client-side navigation. Authenticated account pages identify the
+Supabase user so acquisition can be connected to activation.
+
+Connect the project's Stripe account in Zenovay for authoritative subscription
+revenue attribution. Browser-side revenue events are deliberately not emitted
+from the server redirect that creates the Stripe Checkout session.
